abstract.text: An object to create and manage a Personal VPN configuration.

legalNotices.copyright: Copyright © 2025 Apple Inc. All rights reserved.

inlineContent.text: API gives apps the ability to create and manage a Personal VPN configuration on iOS and macOS. Personal VPN configurations are typically used to provide a service to users that protects their Internet browsing activity on insecure networks such as public Wi-Fi networks.

abstract.text: The API an app can use to create and control a custom system VPN configuration.
